      <section eId="sec_1115_Z">
        <num>1115-Z</num>
        <heading>Limited liability</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_1115_Z__subsec_i">
          <num>(i)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the\nconstruction, ownership, maintenance or operation of any project\nfinanced with the assistance of the authority, (ii) the construction,\nownership, maintenance or operation of any sewerage system or facility\nor water system or facility owned by the water board, or (iii) carrying\nout any of the powers expressly given in this title. Any member of the\nauthority, either appointed by the governor or an employee of the state\nshall be deemed an "employee" for purposes of section eighteen of the\npublic officers law for any actions relating to their activities as a\nmember of the authority created by this state.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
